bound.  This is the identity comparison case used when a capped comparison IP
is built directly for the bounded source optimum's min/max window.
-/
theorem paper_lmms_theorem_3_3_source_min_max_value_pair_forward_ratio_transfer_epsilon
    {SourceAgent SourceItem : Type*}
    [Fintype SourceAgent] [Nonempty SourceAgent]
    {L epsilon : ℝ}
    {optimal : Allocation SourceAgent SourceItem}
    (sourceValue : SourceItem → ℝ)
